                                <para>4.6-5.0V</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col3">
                                <para>Pull up voltage, if no voltage, circuit has open, high resistance, or short to
                                    ground.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="3" spanname="SPAN1">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Connector Resistance Checks to Chassis Ground</emph>
                                    (Turn ignition key OFF. Disconnect sensor connector and negative battery cable.)
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1">
                                <para>2 to gnd</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2">
                                <para>&#60;5&#x2126;</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col3">
                                <para>If >5&#x2126;, check for open ground circuit</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1">
                                <para>1 to gnd</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2">
                                <para>>1k&#x2126;</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col3">
                                <para>If &#60;1k&#x2126;, check for signal circuit short to ground</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="3" spanname="SPAN1">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Harness Resistance Checks</emph>
                                    (Install breakout box on engine harness only.)
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1">
                                <para>X1-6 to 2</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2">
                                <para>&#60;5&#x2126;</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col3">
                                <para>If >5&#x2126;, check for open ground wire</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1">
                                <para>X1-7 to 1</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2">
                                <para>&#60;5&#x2126;</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col3">
                                <para>If>5&#x2126;, check for open signal wire open</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </tbody>
                </tgroup>
            </table>
